body:
### Welcome to CinemaBase.
```
Android mobile application which allows you to browse ratings and descriptions of current top rated movies or search through movie database to find ratings and description of favorite movie titles. Find out what friends are saying about currently rated movies, and leave your own thoughts about movies you have watched.
```
### Authors and Contributors
Daniel Hernandez (@dehernandez7791), and Victor Romero (@...).
